comments: McGee (DAL) firms up in Bey's (ATL) path and marginal lower body contact occurs as the pick is set.
Wood (DAL) establishes his left foot as his pivot and maintains it as he starts his dribble.
Collins (ATL) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during Wood's (DAL) driving shot attempt.
Doncic (DAL) contests Murray's (ATL) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Capela (ATL) jumps alongside Irving's (DAL) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Bey (ATL) establishes himself in Green's (DAL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Young (ATL) receives the pass and hops prior to releasing his dribble.
Wood (DAL) and Bey (ATL) come together off-ball and marginal contact occurs.
Wood (DAL) establishes his left foot as his pivot and maintains it as he starts his dribble.
Capela (ATL) slides under Wood (DAL) while defending his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
After replay review, prior to the touch Capela (ATL) initiates illegal contact with McGee (DAL) as he attempts to get to the pass.
Replay review of the OOB called on McGee (DAL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful.
Doncic (DAL) moves alongside Murray's (ATL) path and legally contests the driving shot attempt.
Bey (ATL) initiates contact with Green's (DAL) body and dislodges him following the rebound.
Murray (ATL) legally contests Irving's (DAL) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Doncic (DAL) brings his hands slightly forward and marginal contact occurs with Young (ATL) during the drive prior to the pass.
Doncic (DAL) legally contests Young's (ATL) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
In an effort to box out, McGee (DAL) extends his left leg backward and makes incidental foot to foot contact with Capela (ATL).
Collins (ATL) deflects the ball out of bounds.
McGee (DAL) initiates contact with Capela (ATL) off-ball that affects his ability to defend the ensuing driving shot attempt.
Doncic (DAL) commits a take foul on Murray (ATL).
Irving (DAL) turns into and delivers contact to Young's (ATL) on the perimeter after attempting the dribble handoff.
Green (DAL) inbounds the ball in under 5 seconds.
Bey (ATL) legally contests Doncic's (DAL) jump shot attempt.
